        {
            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "Looking through the code a little, seems like the cause might be `buffer/nvim_buf_set_name` calling `ex_cmds/rename_buffer` calling `buffer/do_autochdir` calling `file_search/vim_chdirfile` calling `fs/os/os_chdir`.\r\n\r\nWould it be possible to save or store the current working directory in `nvim_buf_set_name`, call `rename_buffer` like normal, and then restore the saved cwd?",
